---
import Layout from '@/components/Layout.astro';
import Container from '@/components/Container.astro';
---
<Layout title="Social Media - Rucking Revolution" description="Connect with the Rucking Revolution community on social media">
  <Container>
    <header class="mb-12 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Connect With Us</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted">
        Join our community across social platforms for daily inspiration, training tips, and community highlights.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Follow Us</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <a href="https://facebook.com/ruckingrevolution" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📘</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Facebook</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">
            Join our community, event announcements, and crew highlights
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://instagram.com/ruckingrevolution" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📸</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Instagram</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">
            Daily training inspiration, community photos, and visual stories
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/ruckingrevolution" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🐦</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Twitter</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">
            Real-time updates, training tips, and community conversations
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://youtube.com/@ruckingrevolution" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📺</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">YouTube</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">
            Training videos, instructional content, and event coverage
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Community Guidelines</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-6">
        We strive to maintain a positive, supportive community across all our social platforms. When engaging with us and other community members, please follow these guidelines:
      </p>
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Be Respectful</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">
            Treat all community members with respect. We're all here to learn, grow, and support each other in our rucking journey.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Stay On Topic</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">
            Keep discussions relevant to rucking, fitness, leadership, and community building. This helps maintain a focused and valuable community.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Share Your Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">
            We love hearing about your rucking journey, training achievements, and crew experiences. Share your stories to inspire others.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">No Spam or Self-Promotion</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">
            Please avoid excessive self-promotion, spam, or unsolicited commercial content. Quality contributions are valued over quantity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What We Share</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Training Content</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted text-sm space-y-2">
            <li>Workout tips and programming</li>
            <li>Form guidance and technique</li>
            <li>Equipment recommendations</li>
            <li>Progressive overload strategies</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Community Stories</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted text-sm space-y-2">
            <li>Crew spotlights and features</li>
            <li>Member achievements and milestones</li>
            <li>Event recaps and photos</li>
            <li>Lessons learned from the field</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Platform Updates</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted text-sm space-y-2">
            <li>New articles and guides</li>
            <li>Feature announcements</li>
            <li>Event and challenge notifications</li>
            <li>Community highlights</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Join the Conversation</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-6">
        Social media is just one way to connect. Here are other ways to get involved:
      </p>
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <a href="/learn/articles" class="block p-4 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">📝 Articles</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Read and share our knowledge base</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/faq" class="block p-4 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">❓ FAQ</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Find answers to common questions</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="block p-4 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">✉️ Contact</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Get in touch with our team</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-gray-50">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Hashtag Movement</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">
          Join the conversation using our official hashtags:
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white rounded-full">#RuckingRevolution</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white rounded-full">#RuckStrong</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white rounded-full">#CarryTheLoad</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white rounded-full">#RuckLife</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </Container>
</Layout>
